                   <div type="textpart" n="B" xml:lang="okz-Latn"><head xml:lang="eng">Face</head>
                   <p>
   <lb n="B1"/>[[pa]]ndval ta kaṁsteṅ {3}
   <lb n="B2"/>mratāñ khloñ guṇa-
                      <lb n="B3"/>[do]ṣa mratāñ khloñ śrī-
                      <lb n="B4"/>[ma]hipativarmma trvāc vraḥ sa-
                      <lb n="B5"/>bhā pre juṁ Āy vraḥ matava-
                      <lb n="B6"/>rana <g ref="sym:bullet-hollow" type="punctuation">.</g> dep vraḥ ka stac Ā-
                      <lb n="B7"/>y vrāc mratāñ khloñ {1}
                      <lb n="B8"/>{1} vihāra mratāñ khloñ
                      <lb n="B9"/>[khlo]ñ glāṅ pvān chmāṁ vraḥ
                      <lb n="B10"/>[pā]ñjiya tamrvāc taṅvā-
                      <lb n="B11"/>y ta pvānn pre Oy khñuṁ bhai pvā-
                      <lb n="B12"/>n ta mratāñ khloñ śrīnare-
                      <lb n="B13"/>ndravijaya thnvar ganā kaṁvrau
                      <lb n="B14"/>ta dau ta kamraṁteṅ Añ
                      <lb n="B15"/>Āy vrāc
   </p>
                   </div>              
</div>
